<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>DIV i z-index</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="position: absolute; top: 130px; left: 100px; z-index: 20">
        Ovaj tekst ima veći z-index pa se prikazuje iznad slike.<br/>
    </div>

    <div style="position: absolute; top: 130px; left: 100px; z-index: 1">
        <img src="flower.jpg" alt="Cvijet" width="220" height="140">
    </div>

    <div style="position: absolute; top: 130px; right: 100px; z-index: 1">
        <img src="horse.jpg" alt="Konj" width="220" height="140">
    </div>
</body>
</html>
